      <title>尼日利亚将使用市场汇率设定丹格特原油销售奈拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/nigeria-to-set-naira-for-dangote-crude-sales-using-market-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚将使用其外汇市场上的本币汇率来结算向非洲最新、最大炼油厂销售的原油，此举平息了外界对尼日利亚将以低于市场奈拉的价格进行交易的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/nigeria-to-set-naira-for-dangote-crude-sales-using-market-rate</guid>
