      <title>美国 30 年期抵押贷款利率一年多来涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/us-30-year-mortgage-rates-climb-by-most-in-more-than-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，美国抵押贷款利率出现 2023 年 7 月以来的最大涨幅，突然停止了长达数月的下滑趋势，这有助于重振房地产活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/us-30-year-mortgage-rates-climb-by-most-in-more-than-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
